Quaternion Function Reference

transpose

Transpose of a quaternion
(Quaternion and octonion overloadings of standard MATLAB® function)

Syntax

Y = X.'

Description

transpose implements the MATLAB® .' operator for quaternion matrices.

See Also

QTFM function: ctranspose
